structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
PUBLIC WORKS IN CITIES OTHER THAN THE FIRST CLASS

law.history: Repealed 1980 Ky. Acts ch. 239, sec. 4, effective July 15, 1980. -- Amended 1976 Ky. Acts ch. 140, sec. 38. -- Amended 1964 Ky. Acts ch. 181, sec. 1. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2741L-1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: City of third, fourth, fifth or sixth class may condemn property for sewerage system under alternate method.
